Go to the https://www.postgresql.org/download/ to download PostgreSQL
The Set up:
Installation Directory: pressvNext->
Select Components: Select everything and press Next->
Data Directory: press Next->
Password: Provide password and and retype then press Next->
Port: press Next->
Advanced options: press Next->
Ready to install: press Next->
Completeing the PostgreSQL Setup Wizard: Check Stack Builder and press Next->
